{"word":"ρυπόομαι","slug":"ρυπόομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ρυπόομαι</b></el> <el>(ρῠπόομαι,) </el><p/><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be foul</i>, <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <el>ρερῠπωμένος</el>, epic for <el>ἐρρυπωμένοι</el>, <i>fouled, soiled</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>ρύ˘πος</el>\n"}]}